oduct操作，延迟从10.4秒激增至9435秒（900倍增长）\n- **影响范围**：该服务被frontend和checkoutservice同时调用，表明是系统级瓶颈\n\n### 2. **次要根因 - redis**\n- cartservice对redis的读写操作延迟显著增加（10-14倍）\n- 这可能与productcatalogservice的异常有关，因为购物车操作需要查询产品信息\n\n### 3. **传播路径分析**\n```\nfrontend → checkoutservice → productcatalogservice (主要瓶颈)\nfrontend → productcatalogservice (直接瓶颈)\ncheckoutservice → cartservice → redis (次要瓶颈)\n```\n\n### 4. **故障影响**\n- **前端服务**：用户请求响应时间从秒级增加到分钟级\n- **结账流程**：PlaceOrder操作完全阻塞，影响核心业务功能\n- **推荐服务**：相对正常，表明问题集中在产品目录和存储层\n\n建议优先检查productcatalogservice的资源使用情况、数据库连接状态以及TiDB集群的健康状况。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "consensus_decision": "AGREED", "current_hypothesis": "productcatalogservice is the root cause due to severe rrt_max latency degradation affecting downstream services"}
